data.description: All of the amenities of a new construction without the wait!  This 3 bedroom / 2.5 bathroom home is less than 2 years old!  Upon entering, you are welcomed by an open floor plan that contains laminate flooring, spacious living room, and quaint kitchen.  This home features all stainless steel appliances, sprinkler system, downstairs half bathroom, attached 1-car garage, upstairs laundry, and a 2nd floor primary bedroom with full bathroom, all situated on a corner lot in Cedar Commons.  Save on the raising costs of electricity with conveying leased solar panels.  What are you waiting for?  Schedule your private showing today, or view this property from the comfort of your own home by viewing the full 360 degree virtual tour!
